headline: Block to Announce First Quarter 2025 Results
summary: DISTRIBUTED-WORK-MODEL/OAKLAND, Calif., April 03, 2025--Block, Inc. (NYSE: XYZ) will release financial results for the first quarter of 2025 on Thursday, May 1, 2025, after market close. Block will also host a conference call and earnings webcast at 2:00 p.m. Pacific Time/5:00 p.m. Eastern Time on the same day to discuss these results.
